23 SECTION 1. Arkansas Code ยง 24-7-1308(b), concerning distribution
24 options under the Teacher Deferred Retirement Option, is amended to add an
25 additional subdivision to read as follows:
26 (3) A member may cancel his or her original election and elect
27 another distribution option under subdivision (b)(1) of this section if the
28 member:
29 (A) Did not elect to receive all or a part of the balance
30 in the plan account as a lump sum payable through an Internal Revenue Code
31 eligible rollover transaction;
32 (B) Has not previously changed his or her election;
33 (C) Cancels his or her election before the end of the
34 second full calendar month immediately following his or her effective
35 retirement date;
36 (D) Files with the system a new distribution election form
